at your left or right?"

1300
01:01:23,760 --> 01:01:25,593
Wow, I wonder who it is.

1301
01:01:25,793 --> 01:01:27,493
(Roaring)

1302
01:01:27,493 --> 01:01:28,626
- Good question!
- Seriously!

1303
01:01:30,126 --> 01:01:34,226
(Ji Seung and Yu Jin on the right,
Ju Hee and Ji Hye on the left)

1304
01:01:34,693 --> 01:01:37,893
What a coincidence.
If one of the guys sat here...

1305
01:01:37,893 --> 01:01:39,726
There are women on both sides.

1306
01:01:39,726 --> 01:01:41,626
Yes, there are two on each side.

1307
01:01:41,993 --> 01:01:43,193
This is so tough.

1308
01:01:43,560 --> 01:01:44,626
I'm curious.

1309
01:01:45,326 --> 01:01:46,726
How are they sitting like that?

1310
01:01:46,726 --> 01:01:47,726
(Si Won sat between the women.)

1311
01:01:48,226 --> 01:01:50,426
He'll pull a killer move after answering.

1312
01:01:51,460 --> 01:01:52,526
She's on my right.

1313
01:01:54,360 --> 01:01:55,726
Si Won is cool.

1314
01:01:56,126 --> 01:01:57,160
He's a cool guy.

1315
01:01:57,160 --> 01:01:58,926
(Ji Seung is on his right
and is his first-impression pick.)

1316
01:01:58,926 --> 01:01:59,926
I see.

1317
01:01:59,926 --> 01:02:02,626
Look at Ji Seung. She's so excited.

1318
01:02:02,626 --> 01:02:03,960
(Those on the right are excited,)

1319
01:02:03,960 --> 01:02:04,960
Okay.

1320
01:02:05,526 --> 01:02:09,293
(while those on the left are disappointed
for no specific reason.)

1321
01:02:09,960 --> 01:02:12,760
(Did Si Won's first-impression pick...)

1322
01:02:12,760 --> 01:02:16,326
(get through to Ji Seung?)

1323
01:02:20,026 --> 01:02:21,093
(Bursting out laughing)

1324
01:02:21,093 --> 01:02:22,126
What is it?

1325
01:02:22,293 --> 01:02:24,460
"A partner who's kind as an angel
but boring."

1326
01:02:25,326 --> 01:02:28,093
"Or a partner who always causes trouble
but gives you a dopamine rush."

1327
01:02:28,093 --> 01:02:30,126
Why don't I get questions like that?

1328
01:02:30,526 --> 01:02:31,993
Ji Hye, answer this too.

1329
01:02:32,760 --> 01:02:33,760
Do it together.

1330
01:02:33,760 --> 01:02:35,526
- I want to answer such questions.
- Answer it together.

1331
01:02:35,526 --> 01:02:37,126
- I'm curious.
- For me,

1332
01:02:37,526 --> 01:02:38,660
it's definitely the former.

1333
01:02:39,360 --> 01:02:41,393
- Kind as an angel but boring?
- I choose the former.

1334
01:02:41,393 --> 01:02:43,726
I like a boring guy.
I can just be the funny one.

1335
01:02:43,726 --> 01:02:44,960
Right, you can.

1336
01:02:44,960 --> 01:02:46,826
I don't think she's funny.

1337
01:02:46,826 --> 01:02:48,260
Come on, don't say that!

1338
01:02:48,693 --> 01:02:52,226
- What's wrong with you?
- Ji Seung hasn't cracked us up yet.

1339
01:02:52,493 --> 01:02:54,326
- What about you, Ji Hye?
- The dopamine guy.

1340
01:02:54,326 --> 01:02:56,026
Okay, but I figured.

1341
01:02:58,893 --> 01:03:02,993
(Ji Seung and Ji Hye have
opposite personalities.)

1342
01:03:05,060 --> 01:03:08,860
- Two first-impression picks.
- Is it "Up and Down?"

1343
01:03:08,860 --> 01:03:11,093
(You have two first-impression picks.
Is your answer up or down?)

1344
01:03:11,093 --> 01:03:12,193
This is easy.

1345
01:03:12,193 --> 01:03:13,226
It is.

1346
01:03:17,126 --> 01:03:18,260
He should go with "down."

1347
01:03:18,860 --> 01:03:19,893
It has to be "down," so...

1348
01:03:19,893 --> 01:03:23,060
- He must pick it to go to Ju Hee.
- You're right.

1349
01:03:23,060 --> 01:03:25,026
You can be strategic with this.

1350
01:03:26,660 --> 01:03:30,026
So you have two first-impression picks?

1351
01:03:30,360 --> 01:03:31,893
But you are all charming.

1352
01:03:34,260 --> 01:03:35,660
He just picks everyone.

1353
01:03:39,993 --> 01:03:41,426
- You like all of them?
- Do you like them all?

1354
01:03:42,793 --> 01:03:43,826
Yes.

1355
01:03:43,826 --> 01:03:45,493
(Does Jin Woo really mean that?)

1356
01:03:45,526 --> 01:03:47,460
- He's really like a younger brother.
- I bet...

1357
01:03:47,460 --> 01:03:49,693
Jin Woo seems to have just reached
the legal age of adulthood.

1358
01:03:50,060 --> 01:03:51,693
Like yesterday.

1359
01:03:51,826 --> 01:03:53,593
(Quickly passing to Yu Jin)

1360
01:03:54,893 --> 01:03:56,293
- What will it be?
- It's so hard.

1361
01:03:57,060 --> 01:03:58,993
This is fun!

1362
01:04:00,193 --> 01:04:02,093
- It feels like a game.
- Yes.

1363
01:04:02,093 --> 01:04:03,826
(They can read each other's feelings
without pressure.)

1364
01:04:05,726 --> 01:04:09,893
"Who seems the most different
from his first impression?"

1365
01:04:14,193 --> 01:04:15,393
It's Yun So.

1366
01:04:15,393 --> 01:04:19,526
(Yun So)

1367
01:04:19,526 --> 01:04:21,026
(Surprised)

1368
01:04:21,026 --> 01:04:23,960
I think he is. He looks cold at first,

1369
01:04:24,960 --> 01:04:27,560
but he'd be really caring
once you get to date him.

1370
01:04:27,960 --> 01:04:29,693
- He'd be so sweet.
- Yes, he'd be warm, sweet,

1371
01:04:29,693 --> 01:04:32,093
and only have eyes
for the person he likes.

1372
01:04:32,093 --> 01:04:33,126
Thank you.

1373
01:04:33,660 --> 01:04:34,660
I think he would.

1374
01:04:36,793 --> 01:04:37,793
Thank you.

1375
01:04:39,460 --> 01:04:40,526
Interesting.

1376
01:04:41,760 --> 01:04:43,726
This looks like a good question.

1377
01:04:43,726 --> 01:04:45,193
- This one?
- Yes.

1378
01:04:45,260 --> 01:04:46,293
You want to get it, Ji Hye?

1379
01:04:46,426 --> 01:04:48,326
- What is it?
- Quick, answer it.

1380
01:04:49,026 --> 01:04:51,326
- What's the question?
- "A physical touch rookie"...

1381
01:04:51,760 --> 01:04:52,960
"versus a physical touch master."

1382
01:04:54,326 --> 01:04:55,860
A master, of course.

1383
01:04:58,160 --> 01:04:59,660
It's clear she's into dopamine.

1384
01:04:59,660 --> 01:05:00,660
She really is a mature woman.

1385
01:05:02,126 --> 01:05:03,260
Obviously.

1386
01:05:05,560 --> 01:05:06,560
I want to ask.

1387
01:05:08,060 --> 01:05:10,660
How good should you be to be a master?

1388
01:05:10,826 --> 01:05:13,493
You keep thinking about it
after you leave.

1389
01:05:13,493 --> 01:05:15,360
- How many times a day?
- Hye Jin, stop.

1390
01:05:15,360 --> 01:05:16,993
- That's enough.
- Why? It pops into your head,

1391
01:05:16,993 --> 01:05:18,393
- and you miss them.
- Just drink your soy milk.

1392
01:05:18,393 --> 01:05:19,426
Fine.

1393
01:05:20,860 --> 01:05:23,760
(The question time
for sharing honest feelings is over.)

1394
01:05:23,960 --> 01:05:25,493
- What time are you going tomorrow?
- Sorry?

1395
01:05:25,826 --> 01:05:26,826
For running.

1396
01:05:27,126 --> 01:05:28,526
Are you running tomorrow?

1397
01:05:28,526 --> 01:05:30,060
- I should start tomorrow.
- You are?

1398
01:05:30,060 --> 01:05:31,160
Are you running every day?

1399
01:05:31,960 --> 01:05:32,960
How far do you run?

1400
01:05:33,126 --> 01:05:34,126
Five kilometers.

1401
01:05:35,060 --> 01:05:36,060
Let me join you.

1402
01:05:37,060 --> 01:05:38,460
Are you okay with six minutes
and 50 seconds?

1403
01:05:39,026 --> 01:05:40,493
Yes, I can adjust to anything.

1404
01:05:40,493 --> 01:05:41,493
Okay.

1405
01:05:42,660 --> 01:05:44,026
Did you bring five workout outfits?

1406
01:05:44,026 --> 01:05:45,860
- I brought seven.
- Seven?

1407
01:05:45,860 --> 01:05:47,460
(Shocked)

1408
01:05:47,460 --> 01:05:49,593
- You're serious about it.
- I'm going all in on running.

1409
01:05:49,860 --> 01:05:51,226
I can run just twice.

1410
01:05:51,226 --> 01:05:53,060
I have two spare sets of workout outfits.

1411
01:05:53,060 --> 01:05:54,060
I'll lend you one.

1412
01:05:54,660 --> 01:05:55,726
You will?

1413
01:05:56,060 --> 01:05:57,126
Good idea.

1414
01:05:57,126 --> 01:05:58,160
Are you okay with...

1415
01:05:58,160 --> 01:05:59,493
- cropped zip-up and leggings?
- That's cool.

1416
01:05:59,493 --> 01:06:00,993
- Are you sure?
- I like it.

1417
01:06:00,993 --> 01:06:02,526
I also have two workout outfits.

1418
01:06:02,526 --> 01:06:04,026
I'll lend you some.

1419
01:06:04,026 --> 01:06:05,060
Gosh.

1420
01:06:08,360 --> 01:06:09,460
This startles me.

1421
01:06:09,926 --> 01:06:13,926
(A message arrives at the Yeon House.)

1422
01:06:14,960 --> 01:06:17,893
(Leave an anonymous Love QR
to your pick back in your room.)

1423
01:06:17,893 --> 01:06:19,426
Finally, a Love QR!

1424
01:06:22,360 --> 01:06:23,493
It's really happening.

1425
01:06:24,026 --> 01:06:25,826
It's suddenly getting tough.

1426
01:06:26,326 --> 01:06:27,460
This is fun...

1427
01:06:27,626 --> 01:06:29,760
because you just don't send texts.

1428
01:06:29,760 --> 01:06:32,460
You can also send videos, photos,
and voice messages.

1429
01:06:32,493 --> 01:06:33,760
- You can send anything.
- Right.

1430
01:06:35,193 --> 01:06:38,426
(Who will receive the Love QRs...)

1431
01:06:38,426 --> 01:06:42,360
(from the older women and younger guys?)

1432
01:06:43,160 --> 01:06:45,160
(Si Won and Yun So's room)

1433
01:06:45,160 --> 01:06:47,960
I'm dying to know who Jin Woo picked.

1434
01:06:48,826 --> 01:06:51,393
I wonder what he'll do
or what he's thinking about.

1435
01:06:52,093 --> 01:06:54,260
They both like Ju Hee.

1436
01:06:54,660 --> 01:06:56,426
Yes. Honestly,

1437
01:06:56,760 --> 01:06:59,260
- I don't get why he chose her there.
- Exactly.

1438
01:06:59,626 --> 01:07:01,693
- Suddenly?
- I think he kept her...

1439
01:07:01,693 --> 01:07:03,160
as his second choice.

1440
01:07:03,493 --> 01:07:06,426
He said all four of them were charming.

1441
01:07:06,460 --> 01:07:08,260
I guess he's keeping all options open.

1442
01:07:08,260 --> 01:07:10,393
He probably thinks
of meeting everyone at least once.

1443
01:07:11,926 --> 01:07:14,093
I should take photos now.

1444
01:07:14,093 --> 01:07:15,426
Can we take them here?

1445
01:07:16,093 --> 01:07:17,126
Well.

1446
01:07:17,593 --> 01:07:18,593
There's nothing to shoot.

1447
01:07:18,593 --> 01:07:20,926
- Then let's go out and take photos.
- Shall we?

1448
01:07:20,926 --> 01:07:22,793
- Yes.
- Are you coming with me?

1449
01:07:22,793 --> 01:07:23,826
Yes.

1450
01:07:23,993 --> 01:07:25,593
(Clicking)

1451
01:07:25,593 --> 01:07:28,226
I can't wait.
This is quite fun to watch too.

1452
01:07:28,660 --> 01:07:29,726
I'll be right back.

1453
01:07:34,126 --> 01:07:36,060
Are you here for photos?

1454
01:07:36,060 --> 01:07:37,093
Where are you going?

1455
01:07:37,893 --> 01:07:38,993
(Taking photos without a word)

1456
01:07:39,526 --> 01:07:40,893
They're working so hard.

1457
01:07:41,660 --> 01:07:43,926
I kind of get it, though.

1458
01:07:44,560 --> 01:07:46,726
Wait. How do you get it?

1459
01:07:47,026 --> 01:07:48,960
What photos do I send?

1460
01:07:48,960 --> 01:07:50,493
(Meanwhile, the women)

1461
01:07:50,826 --> 01:07:52,760
Is it not what you expected at first?

1462
01:07:52,760 --> 01:07:53,860
It's a bit different for me.

1463
01:07:53,860 --> 01:07:56,793
- Me too.
- It's more like "Truth or Dare."

1464
01:07:56,793 --> 01:07:58,826
- Does it feel different afterward?
- Yes.

1465
01:07:59,093 --> 01:08:00,860
- If anything.
- Really?

1466
01:08:00,860 --> 01:08:02,460
(Have her feelings changed
after the question card time?)

1467
01:08:02,660 --> 01:08:05,126
- I had to think for around five minutes.
- Me too.

1468
01:08:05,126 --> 01:08:07,293
So when the guys...

1469
01:08:07,293 --> 01:08:10,226
picked so quickly,

1470
01:08:10,226 --> 01:08:12,126
I was really surprised.

1471
01:08:13,426 --> 01:08:15,660
I guess it's just this.

1472
01:08:15,660 --> 01:08:18,860
Don't think too much
and focus on this moment.

1473
01:08:18,860 --> 01:08:21,326
Choose the one
who attracted you more today.

1474
01:08:21,326 --> 01:08:23,026
- Today?
- Today.

1475
01:08:23,026 --> 01:08:24,460
(Maybe send it to the person
you were most drawn to.)

1476
01:08:24,460 --> 01:08:27,093
(Ji Hye and Ju Hee's room)

1477
01:08:27,093 --> 01:08:28,093
This is so hard.

1478
01:08:29,360 --> 01:08:30,460
This is so hard.

1479
01:08:33,626 --> 01:08:35,226
Don't you think it's hard...

1480
01:08:35,226 --> 01:08:36,293
- since we still don't know yet?
- Yes.

1481
01:08:36,293 --> 01:08:39,260
- Right?
- We might have to wait until tomorrow...

1482
01:08:40,093 --> 01:08:43,260
to find out.

1483
01:08:43,260 --> 01:08:45,060
It's too early.

1484
01:08:46,460 --> 01:08:48,560
- They're so serious.
- Is it supposed to be this hard?

1485
01:08:48,561 --> 01:08:51,211
(Women are deep in thought unlike guys.)

1486
01:08:51,346 --> 01:08:52,346
Should this be this tough?

1487
01:08:57,226 --> 01:08:59,460
(A Love QR has arrived.)

1488
01:08:59,460 --> 01:09:00,893
It's the time.

1489
01:09:00,893 --> 01:09:06,028
(Go to the QR room
and find out the sender's feelings.)

1490
01:09:16,572 --> 01:09:18,605
(The secret space is finally open.)

1491
01:09:18,606 --> 01:09:20,910
Let's go. I can't wait.

1492
01:09:24,508 --> 01:09:29,107
(Prepared inside the QR Room is...)

1493
01:09:29,108 --> 01:09:33,552
(each participant's Love QR.)

1494
01:09:35,226 --> 01:09:40,696
(Scanning one's own QR...)

1495
01:09:41,705 --> 01:09:44,934
(allows them to check
the messages sent to them.)

1496
01:09:45,567 --> 01:09:48,937
(Did they manage
to connect with each other?)

1497
01:09:49,243 --> 01:09:52,607
That was the very place where
laughter and tears crossed paths.

1498
01:09:53,156 --> 01:09:56,478
Utilizing a QR code is quite innovative
because they can also send videos.

1499
01:09:56,702 --> 01:09:59,715
They could imagine all sorts of things,
wondering what it could possibly be.

1500
01:10:01,350 --> 01:10:05,131
(The one heading
to the QR Room first is...)

1501
01:10:05,132 --> 01:10:08,714
(Yu Jin.)

1502
01:10:16,384 --> 01:10:20,090
(Yu Jin received two votes
in the first impression vote...)

1503
01:10:20,091 --> 01:10:22,438
(from Jun Han and Jin Woo.)

1504
01:10:25,917 --> 01:10:31,614
(How many QRs did Yu Jin receive?)

1505
01:10:37,260 --> 01:10:44,350
(Yu Jin cautiously scans her QR.)

1506
01:10:45,051 --> 01:10:46,057
What could it be?

1507
01:10:46,058 --> 01:10:47,931
(Did she receive two votes
just like the first impression vote?)

1508
01:10:58,371 --> 01:10:59,027
Let's take a guess.

1509
01:10:59,028 --> 01:11:00,540
(How many guys would've voted for her?)

1510
01:11:00,541 --> 01:11:02,769
- How many?
- I say Jun Han and Jin Woo.

1511
01:11:03,162 --> 01:11:05,322
My prediction is that...

1512
01:11:06,782 --> 01:11:08,534
Jun Han might have changed his mind...

1513
01:11:08,535 --> 01:11:10,263
since it was interesting
to talk with Ji Hye.

1514
01:11:10,264 --> 01:11:11,818
- Do you really think so?
- Jin Woo also...

1515
01:11:11,819 --> 01:11:14,617
might have also chosen Ju Hee
instead of Yu Jin.

1516
01:11:14,618 --> 01:11:16,817
- I'm sure Jun Han voted for her.
- Really?

1517
01:11:17,878 --> 01:11:20,480
What do you think? How many votes
do you think Yu Jin will get?

1518
01:11:21,221 --> 01:11:23,236
She will definitely get
at least two votes.

1519
01:11:23,416 --> 01:11:25,972
- Does that include your own vote as well?
- My own vote?

1520
01:11:26,869 --> 01:11:28,776
If I include my own vote,
it would be three votes.

1521
01:11:29,229 --> 01:11:34,597
(How many Love QRs
did Yu Jin actually receive?)

1522
01:11:36,275 --> 01:11:40,207
- What?
- Maybe there's none. I'm telling you.

1523
01:11:40,208 --> 01:11:42,709
No way. Yu Jin definitely got some.

1524
01:11:47,346 --> 01:11:50,483
(You have received no Love QR.)

1525
01:11:50,598 --> 01:11:51,765
(Shocked)

1526
01:11:51,766 --> 01:11:54,253
See? I told you she didn't have any.

1527
01:11:55,044 --> 01:11:56,489
- How can this be possible?
- This doesn't make any sense.

1528
01:11:57,351 --> 01:12:00,917
- Then, what about my vote?
- Yu Jin was nice to everyone.

1529
01:12:01,457 --> 01:12:06,663
Jun Han was probably attracted to Ji Hye
because she casually tossed him attention.

1530
01:12:06,949 --> 01:12:11,738
- So, Jun Han cast his vote for Ji Hye?
- Jin Woo led...

1531
01:12:12,014 --> 01:12:15,635
- a one-on-one conversation earlier.
- Did he vote for Ju Hee then?

1532
01:12:15,636 --> 01:12:16,743
Yes.

1533
01:12:17,361 --> 01:12:19,005
I completely understand
the psychology of younger men.

1534
01:12:19,006 --> 01:12:19,973
(He has a Younger guy PhD.)

1535
01:12:20,574 --> 01:12:23,393
- DinDin, please teach me later.
- No problem.

1536
01:12:23,394 --> 01:12:24,953
I caught on to the situation immediately.

1537
01:12:25,119 --> 01:12:27,086
DinDin is absolutely amazing.

1538
01:12:28,166 --> 01:12:32,158
(Yu Jin did not receive a QR from anyone.)

1539
01:12:32,832 --> 01:12:33,818
Well,

1540
01:12:34,098 --> 01:12:35,891
all right.

1541
01:12:37,791 --> 01:12:39,171
Oh, no.

1542
01:12:42,042 --> 01:12:43,750
It's okay.

1543
01:12:44,249 --> 01:12:46,272
I can receive many votes in the future.

1544
01:12:49,922 --> 01:12:52,348
Yu Jin used to smile so brightly
before this happened.

1545
01:12:55,014 --> 01:12:56,649
(Glancing)

1546
01:13:02,007 --> 01:13:03,819
(Yu Jin ranked first in the first
impression vote but got no QR.)

1547
01:13:03,820 --> 01:13:06,799
- It's so shocking, seriously.
- How can this happen?

1548
01:13:10,765 --> 01:13:11,765
I'll be back.

1549
01:13:18,931 --> 01:13:22,370
(Jun Han got the most votes
in the first impression vote.)

1550
01:13:22,371 --> 01:13:23,636
He was the popular guy.

1551
01:13:29,396 --> 01:13:34,488
(How many Love QRs did he get?)

1552
01:13:35,915 --> 01:13:36,915
Wow.

1553
01:13:42,727 --> 01:13:43,727
Please.

1554
01:13:47,686 --> 01:13:48,686
Please.

1555
01:13:52,205 --> 01:13:55,464
(He's extremely nervous
checking his first Love QR.)

1556
01:13:55,465 --> 01:13:56,465
Please.

1557
01:14:04,990 --> 01:14:06,686
(Startled)

1558
01:14:06,788 --> 01:14:09,422
I think he probably received votes
from Yu Jin and Ji Hye again.

1559
01:14:10,275 --> 01:14:13,426
I also think he must have
definitely received a vote from Ji Hye.

1560
01:14:15,101 --> 01:14:19,198
(How many Love QRs did Jun Han get?)

1561
01:14:21,253 --> 01:14:23,799
(You have received no Love QR.)

1562
01:14:23,946 --> 01:14:26,439
- Hold on. Maybe it's not updated yet.
- That's ridiculous.

1563
01:14:26,566 --> 01:14:29,709
Jun Han didn't receive any either?

1564
01:14:30,545 --> 01:14:32,445
I guess it's something like this.

1565
01:14:32,705 --> 01:14:36,215
Since he seems too smooth and experienced,
the ladies might feel...

1566
01:14:36,317 --> 01:14:39,919
that he is not exactly the type
of younger man they expected.

1567
01:14:40,191 --> 01:14:41,614
Are you saying that the flutter has gone?

1568
01:14:42,416 --> 01:14:44,517
Then, who did Yu Jin vote for,

1569
01:14:44,518 --> 01:14:47,253
looking so disappointed
that no one chose her?

1570
01:14:47,254 --> 01:14:48,040
You're right.

1571
01:14:48,235 --> 01:14:49,710
What happened?

1572
01:14:49,729 --> 01:14:51,904
Neither of them has a reason
to be disappointed, then.

1573
01:14:51,924 --> 01:14:53,582
But they're both so disappointed.

1574
01:14:56,414 --> 01:14:57,414
Hold on.

1575
01:14:59,580 --> 01:15:03,176
(He checks his Love QR again
due to the unexpected result.)

1576
01:15:04,866 --> 01:15:07,447
(But the result stays the same.)

1577
01:15:08,772 --> 01:15:09,772
There's nothing.

1578
01:15:15,801 --> 01:15:17,657
I really never expected to get zero votes.

1579
01:15:18,341 --> 01:15:20,627
I was so shocked
as soon as I received the result.

1580
01:15:22,441 --> 01:15:27,920
I was devastated.

1581
01:15:29,046 --> 01:15:31,532
I think joking around too much
during our first meeting...

1582
01:15:32,345 --> 01:15:34,974
made me appear a bit insincere.

1583
01:15:35,758 --> 01:15:38,711
The ladies might have indeed
perceived him that way.

1584
01:15:39,404 --> 01:15:42,381
You look like a classic beauty.
Miss Pretty.

1585
01:15:43,417 --> 01:15:45,185
Can you kiss a boyfriend
who has just eaten green onions?

1586
01:15:46,090 --> 01:15:47,090
Everyone has a beautiful smile.

1587
01:15:47,091 --> 01:15:49,688
(Jun Han made light jokes
to get close quickly.)

1588
01:15:49,689 --> 01:15:50,890
I'm honored to be with pretty ladies.

1589
01:15:51,063 --> 01:15:56,902
(Did Jun Han's behavior
make him appear a bit insincere?)

1590
01:15:57,288 --> 01:15:59,865
Since I naturally have a playful image,

1591
01:16:00,533 --> 01:16:03,035
I thought I should use it
to show off my charms.

1592
01:16:03,634 --> 01:16:04,574
It backfired,

1593
01:16:04,575 --> 01:16:06,932
making me look too insincere
for a first impression.

1594
01:16:08,540 --> 01:16:11,526
I deeply regret making those remarks.

1595
01:16:12,392 --> 01:16:13,980
Oh, no.

1596
01:16:13,981 --> 01:16:16,549
(He looks back on the moments
he regrets now.)

1597
01:16:17,730 --> 01:16:19,518
Okay. Let's try harder.

1598
01:16:21,763 --> 01:16:24,490
They were the popular ones.

1599
01:16:26,626 --> 01:16:30,930
(The third one to check the QR is Ji Hye.)

1600
01:16:32,065 --> 01:16:36,672
(Ji Hye got no votes
for the first impression vote.)

1601
01:16:37,770 --> 01:16:40,553
(Can she get a different result
this time?)

1602
01:16:40,554 --> 01:16:42,208
She could get four votes.

1603
01:16:50,450 --> 01:16:52,319
(Trembling)

1604
01:16:54,438 --> 01:16:57,724
Since I received zero votes
during the first impression vote,

1605
01:16:58,391 --> 01:17:01,928
I was so scared to check the QR.

1606
01:17:07,289 --> 01:17:11,371
(She checks her Love QR
with a trembling heart.)

1607
01:17:17,235 --> 01:17:19,412
(You have received two Love QRs.)

1608
01:17:19,560 --> 01:17:24,016
- Two people!
- Congratulations!

1609
01:17:24,286 --> 01:17:27,053
See? You never know.

1610
01:17:27,866 --> 01:17:30,923
(Ji Hye was chosen by two younger guys.)

1611
01:17:31,965 --> 01:17:33,926
(Grinning)

1612
01:17:34,740 --> 01:17:36,662
I managed to restore
my self-esteem at that moment.

1613
01:17:36,997 --> 01:17:38,491
I realized that I still have
what it takes.

1614
01:17:39,097 --> 01:17:40,332
She's so happy.

1615
01:17:40,733 --> 01:17:43,069
(What's the first QR
that arrived for her?)

1616
01:17:47,195 --> 01:17:49,882
- What is that?
- "You must be tired. Sleep tight."

1617
01:17:52,115 --> 01:17:52,948
(What's this?)

1618
01:17:52,949 --> 01:17:54,493
Who can tell just from that?

1619
01:17:56,141 --> 01:18:01,400
I think he took a photo of the view
from his room and sent it to me.

1620
01:18:02,758 --> 01:18:07,696
(What is the second Love QR she received?)

1621
01:18:08,890 --> 01:18:09,769
Yeon House?

1622
01:18:09,770 --> 01:18:12,390
It looks like the signpost
at the entrance.

1623
01:18:16,516 --> 01:18:18,474
I really don't know who this is.

1624
01:18:18,728 --> 01:18:20,208
I have absolutely no idea.

1625
01:18:20,355 --> 01:18:21,777
I don't even have a clue.

1626
01:18:22,336 --> 01:18:23,145
Seriously.

1627
01:18:28,236 --> 01:18:29,576
(Snap)

1628
01:18:31,276 --> 01:18:35,045
My first impression of Yu Jin
was really good.

1629
01:18:35,424 --> 01:18:39,428
But visually, Ji Hye is much closer
to my ideal type.

1630
01:18:40,123 --> 01:18:44,256
Ji Hye said that dopamine is
what matters in a relationship.

1631
01:18:44,596 --> 01:18:46,756
Since Yeon House stands for dopamine,

1632
01:18:46,807 --> 01:18:48,922
I took a picture of the "Yeon House" sign.

1633
01:18:49,563 --> 01:18:50,783
It's a total dopamine rush itself.

1634
01:18:50,784 --> 01:18:53,523
(Ji Hye's second QR was a photo
sent by Jun Han.)

1635
01:18:53,942 --> 01:18:57,268
(Then who could have sent the first QR?)

1636
01:18:57,402 --> 01:18:59,122
Who could that be?

1637
01:19:00,041 --> 01:19:00,916
Si Won?

1638
01:19:01,296 --> 01:19:02,117
It's Jin Woo.

1639
01:19:02,382 --> 01:19:03,676
- I think it's Jin Woo.
- Yes.

1640
01:19:04,406 --> 01:19:06,088
Or is it Yun So?

1641
01:19:06,089 --> 01:19:07,155
(First Love QR)

1642
01:19:07,155 --> 01:19:11,244
(The sender of the QR is hard to guess.)

1643
01:19:12,916 --> 01:19:15,831
I'm just grateful if anyone sends me one.

1644
01:19:16,509 --> 01:19:18,900
I'm going to get to know everyone
one by one.

1645
01:19:19,682 --> 01:19:21,170
I want to talk to everyone a lot.

1646
01:19:21,195 --> 01:19:22,359
Among them,

1647
01:19:22,383 --> 01:19:25,712
I think I'll choose the person
who's the most fun, easy to talk to,

1648
01:19:25,736 --> 01:19:27,442
and has the best chemistry.

1649
01:19:30,070 --> 01:19:33,838
(The next guest in the QR Room is Ju Hee.)

1650
01:19:36,788 --> 01:19:40,463
(Ju Hee, who received
one first impression vote from Yun So)

1651
01:19:49,965 --> 01:19:51,551
(Did she receive a Love QR this time too?)

1652
01:19:51,576 --> 01:19:52,868
I think Jin Woo will be there.

1653
01:19:59,491 --> 01:20:00,691
No, there are two.

1654
01:20:00,692 --> 01:20:01,667
Jin Woo and Yun So went.

1655
01:20:01,668 --> 01:20:03,288
I also think Jin Woo will be there.

1656
01:20:03,702 --> 01:20:05,681
No, I think Yun So sent his vote here.

1657
01:20:13,982 --> 01:20:15,482
(You have received one Love QR.)

1658
01:20:15,490 --> 01:20:16,750
I think it's Yun So.

1659
01:20:17,039 --> 01:20:17,910
- It's Yun So.
- Yun So?

1660
01:20:17,911 --> 01:20:19,294
You're doing great.

1661
01:20:19,295 --> 01:20:21,808
(Smiling)

1662
01:20:24,604 --> 01:20:25,846
Perilla oil kimchi stew?

1663
01:20:25,871 --> 01:20:27,436
They cooked together earlier.

1664
01:20:27,437 --> 01:20:28,196
Right.

1665
01:20:32,582 --> 01:20:37,276
He took a picture
of the kimchi stew packaging and sent it.

1666
01:20:37,955 --> 01:20:40,115
I have absolutely no idea who it is.

1667
01:20:40,929 --> 01:20:41,583
Pardon?

1668
01:20:42,329 --> 01:20:43,972
What's wrong with her now?

1669
01:20:44,228 --> 01:20:45,842
But actually,

1670
01:20:45,843 --> 01:20:49,069
Yun So expressed his feelings
very directly only to Ju Hee.

1671
01:20:49,116 --> 01:20:51,259
- He didn't do that to the others.
- Right.

1672
01:20:52,654 --> 01:20:55,671
(Who is the younger man
who sent the kimchi stew photo?)

1673
01:20:55,672 --> 01:20:56,975
It's Yun So.

1674
01:20:57,136 --> 01:21:00,096
I sent my QR to Ju Hee.

1675
01:21:00,442 --> 01:21:01,770
I should send it like this.

1676
01:21:02,975 --> 01:21:04,870
There's some residual heat left.

1677
01:21:04,877 --> 01:21:08,915
(They struggled because the seasoning
in the stew wouldn't dissolve properly.)

1678
01:21:08,954 --> 01:21:14,039
We once put a seasoning ring
into the kimchi stew.

1679
01:21:14,182 --> 01:21:17,240
Since that feels like the starting point
for the two of us,

1680
01:21:17,264 --> 01:21:20,159
I took a picture of the seasoning ring
and sent it.

1681
01:21:20,160 --> 01:21:21,133
(It is a symbol of a new beginning.)

1682
01:21:21,282 --> 01:21:23,892
But the person involved doesn't even know.

1683
01:21:24,263 --> 01:21:26,461
- Why doesn't she know?
- Because she's not interested.

1684
01:21:27,302 --> 01:21:28,831
That makes sense.

1685
01:21:29,771 --> 01:21:33,757
(Is Ju Hee really not interested
in Yun So?)

1686
01:21:34,736 --> 01:21:40,018
(Where did Ju Hee's Love QR go?)

1687
01:21:40,308 --> 01:21:44,711
(Next up is Jin Woo, who got 0 votes
in the first impression vote.)

1688
01:21:44,712 --> 01:21:47,011
Now, how many QRs did he receive?

1689
01:21:54,756 --> 01:21:57,364
(Sighs)

1690
01:22:00,666 --> 01:22:02,792
- Come on.
- Zero again?

1691
01:22:02,793 --> 01:22:04,612
- I think it'll be zero.
- Something feels off.

1692
01:22:06,002 --> 01:22:08,717
I don't think he received any.
I have a feeling.

1693
01:22:08,718 --> 01:22:11,263
Maybe he received one from Ju Hee?

1694
01:22:13,775 --> 01:22:16,003
(Smirks)

1695
01:22:18,680 --> 01:22:19,947
(You have received no Love QR.)

1696
01:22:19,948 --> 01:22:22,228
Poor Jin Woo.

1697
01:22:24,268 --> 01:22:25,904
I already had a bad feeling...

1698
01:22:25,928 --> 01:22:27,438
because I didn't get
any first impression votes.

1699
01:22:27,439 --> 01:22:28,459
Something felt off.

1700
01:22:29,774 --> 01:22:31,994
Seeing the heartbreaking results,

1701
01:22:32,581 --> 01:22:34,396
I was down all day.

1702
01:22:34,715 --> 01:22:35,855
Oh, Jin Woo.

1703
01:22:40,356 --> 01:22:42,302
I think I'm only popular among flies.

1704
01:22:43,489 --> 01:22:45,373
I can't watch this.

1705
01:22:45,373 --> 01:22:47,484
(Jin Woo trying to crack a joke)

1706
01:22:48,610 --> 01:22:52,712
(Returning to the room
with mixed feelings)

1707
01:23:00,589 --> 01:23:03,340
(Sighs)

1708
01:23:05,193 --> 01:23:07,350
(Sighs)

1709
01:23:10,065 --> 01:23:11,479
(Sighs)

1710
01:23:11,479 --> 01:23:14,079
It's so sad to watch Jin Woo.

1711
01:23:15,570 --> 01:23:20,241
(Continuous sighing)

1712
01:23:22,490 --> 01:23:24,074
Starting tomorrow,

1713
01:23:24,158 --> 01:23:29,017
I think I should take the initiative
to talk more.

1714
01:23:30,118 --> 01:23:32,874
(The younger man Jin Woo strengthens
his resolve for tomorrow.)

1715
01:23:32,874 --> 01:23:34,727
He needs to shake that off quickly.

1716
01:23:37,116 --> 01:23:39,121
The older women didn't vote for him
at all?

1717
01:23:39,122 --> 01:23:40,772
Not a single one. Two men with zero votes.

1718
01:23:42,164 --> 01:23:46,088
(The sixth visitor to the QR Room,
the younger man Yun So)

1719
01:23:48,165 --> 01:23:49,737
I'm so curious.

1720
01:23:49,738 --> 01:23:52,414
(Who did Yun So receive a QR from?)

1721
01:23:57,295 --> 01:23:58,567
(Sighs)

1722
01:23:58,568 --> 01:24:03,161
Yun So could have 4 votes right now or 0.

1723
01:24:03,162 --> 01:24:04,722
(Taking a deep breath and scanning the QR)

1724
01:24:14,735 --> 01:24:15,597
Huh?

1725
01:24:18,853 --> 01:24:20,257
Scanning it one more time?

1726
01:24:20,258 --> 01:24:22,652
- There's none?
- It's Si Won, then.

1727
01:24:22,653 --> 01:24:23,826
(Are the remaining votes all for Si Won?)

1728
01:24:26,293 --> 01:24:28,685
(You have received three Love QRs.)

1729
01:24:28,686 --> 01:24:30,255
(Wow)

1730
01:24:30,256 --> 01:24:31,213
Three people?

1731
01:24:31,868 --> 01:24:33,247
What did Yun So actually do?

1732
01:24:34,629 --> 01:24:36,852
As expected, it's that.

1733
01:24:36,936 --> 01:24:38,440
- As expected.
- What is it?

1734
01:24:38,836 --> 01:24:39,905
Just being steadfast?

1735
01:24:40,235 --> 01:24:41,422
- Not showing off?
- Right.

1736
01:24:41,729 --> 01:24:47,432
Because he might be
the exact opposite of Jun Han,

1737
01:24:47,433 --> 01:24:49,578
who got zero votes.

1738
01:24:49,634 --> 01:24:50,699
Right.

1739
01:24:50,724 --> 01:24:53,836
"The others are a bit playful,
but this guy is steadfast."

1740
01:24:53,837 --> 01:24:55,836
There could be something like that.

1741
01:25:01,148 --> 01:25:03,111
Honestly, I really didn't expect it.

1742
01:25:03,795 --> 01:25:07,052
I was flustered that I got three,

1743
01:25:07,394 --> 01:25:09,251
but I'm grateful.

1744
01:25:10,685 --> 01:25:13,655
(What is the first Love QR?)

1745
01:25:16,618 --> 01:25:18,398
She sent a photo of workout outfits?

1746
01:25:18,399 --> 01:25:20,127
(Someone's workout outfits photo)

1747
01:25:26,936 --> 01:25:30,272
(What is the second QR Yun So received?)

1748
01:25:30,680 --> 01:25:32,035
"I'll look forward to the swimming pool."

1749
01:25:32,036 --> 01:25:33,942
They must have talked
about the swimming pool.

1750
01:25:35,242 --> 01:25:36,422
(Snickers)

1751
01:25:37,078 --> 01:25:40,833
(What is the meaning
of Yun So's laughter?)

1752
01:25:41,216 --> 01:25:44,358
(The last QR for Yun So)

1753
01:25:44,593 --> 01:25:46,931
"I want to go for a walk together."

1754
01:25:46,956 --> 01:25:48,523
"Go for a walk together." Who could it be?

1755
01:25:52,394 --> 01:25:56,885
(The last QR is someone
asking him out on a date.)

1756
01:25:59,646 --> 01:26:01,646
Congratulations, Yun So.

1757
01:26:01,647 --> 01:26:03,267
(Yun So received Love QRs
from 3 older women.)

1758
01:26:03,871 --> 01:26:06,262
I kind of expected Yu Jin,

1759
01:26:06,263 --> 01:26:08,577
but I really didn't expect the others.

1760
01:26:09,022 --> 01:26:12,424
Yu Jin seems to really love running,
so I think it's Yu Jin.

1761
01:26:14,993 --> 01:26:16,940
(The first QR
with the workout outfits photo...)

1762
01:26:16,941 --> 01:26:18,062
(was Yu Jin's message.)

1763
01:26:18,786 --> 01:26:20,501
Then shall we go
for a light three-kilometer run?

1764
01:26:20,502 --> 01:26:23,206
I can run just twice.
I have two spare sets of workout outfits.

1765
01:26:23,255 --> 01:26:24,659
Really? I'll lend you some.

1766
01:26:25,172 --> 01:26:26,494
Seriously?

1767
01:26:26,765 --> 01:26:27,696
That sounds good.

1768
01:26:28,239 --> 01:26:30,753
When we talk,

1769
01:26:31,184 --> 01:26:32,834
he's very witty.

1770
01:26:33,305 --> 01:26:34,569
I want to get to know him.

1771
01:26:34,594 --> 01:26:35,904
Do we have good chemistry?

1772
01:26:35,905 --> 01:26:37,548
I want to check that out too.

1773
01:26:38,373 --> 01:26:41,807
(The workout outfits photo
was Yu Jin's QR.)

1774
01:26:42,325 --> 01:26:47,382
The swimsuit one must be Ji Hye,
who loves dopamine the most.

1775
01:26:48,686 --> 01:26:52,521
I sent my Love QR to Yun So.

1776
01:26:55,053 --> 01:26:56,057
Shall I go first?

1777
01:26:56,419 --> 01:26:58,393
My name is Lee Yun So.

1778
01:26:58,394 --> 01:27:03,122
At first, I thought he looked very cold.

1779
01:27:03,123 --> 01:27:03,954
But...

1780
01:27:04,374 --> 01:27:06,468
Would you like a Coke?

1781
01:27:07,002 --> 01:27:07,978
Would you like a Coke?

1782
01:27:07,979 --> 01:27:09,304
(Spilling)

1783
01:27:09,329 --> 01:27:11,166
Would you like a Coke?

1784
01:27:11,191 --> 01:27:12,811
- Oh, I'm sorry.
- Is that how you hand it over?

1785
01:27:12,909 --> 01:27:13,821
She finds it cute.

1786
01:27:13,846 --> 01:27:16,985
I saw a bit of his clumsy side,
so I was curious.

1787
01:27:17,046 --> 01:27:22,166
If we meet and talk,
I think I might find him cute.

1788
01:27:22,167 --> 01:27:24,036
He has those kinds of charms.

1789
01:27:24,938 --> 01:27:26,221
Please make sure to eat some rice.

1790
01:27:26,799 --> 01:27:27,635
I don't eat it.

1791
01:27:27,636 --> 01:27:29,080
- You said you don't eat rice.
- Yes.

1792
01:27:29,224 --> 01:27:33,695
He's cutting off carbs
and dieting right now.

1793
01:27:33,696 --> 01:27:35,853
So it sparked my curiosity,

1794
01:27:35,902 --> 01:27:39,234
and I thought it would be fun
to go on a date together.

1795
01:27:39,753 --> 01:27:41,742
("Yun So, I'll look forward
to the swimming pool.")

1796
01:27:41,743 --> 01:27:44,003
(It was the QR sent
by dopamine lover Ji Hye.)

1797
01:27:44,779 --> 01:27:47,027
(And the third Love QR Yun So received)

1798
01:27:47,028 --> 01:27:48,690
("I want to go for a walk together.")

1799
01:27:49,256 --> 01:27:50,445
Who is it?

1800
01:27:52,682 --> 01:27:55,417
"Go for a walk together"...

1801
01:27:56,449 --> 01:27:58,053
He can't figure out
who the last person is.

1802
01:27:58,078 --> 01:27:59,821
- Could it be Ji Seung?
- "A walk?"

1803
01:28:01,336 --> 01:28:02,247
Ju Hee?

1804
01:28:05,585 --> 01:28:10,518
I wanted to talk to Yun So,

1805
01:28:10,519 --> 01:28:12,362
so I sent my QR to him.

1806
01:28:12,363 --> 01:28:13,286
Right, right.

1807
01:28:13,287 --> 01:28:16,244
I wanted to chat while taking a walk.

1808
01:28:16,703 --> 01:28:19,194
They say it will be warm tomorrow,

1809
01:28:19,218 --> 01:28:25,079
so I sent the QR to suggest a walk
in the afternoon.

1810
01:28:26,145 --> 01:28:27,394
Right. You did well.

1811
01:28:27,394 --> 01:28:29,075
(The last Love QR was Ju Hee's message)

1812
01:28:29,076 --> 01:28:30,831
("I want to go for a walk together.")

1813
01:28:31,515 --> 01:28:32,833
(Ju Hee and Yun So)

1814
01:28:32,834 --> 01:28:34,983
(Both their first impressions and Love QRs
were directed at each other.)

1815
01:28:36,240 --> 01:28:41,710
(Then, who is the older woman
Jin Woo sent his Love QR to?)

1816
01:28:44,765 --> 01:28:46,283
(It was Ji Hye,
whom he had handed a strawberry.)

1817
01:28:46,283 --> 01:28:48,445
- Have a strawberry.
- Yeah, thank you.

1818
01:28:48,724 --> 01:28:50,390
- Right.
- Is it Ji Hye?

1819
01:28:50,421 --> 01:28:52,246
Giving her that strawberry took
a lot of courage,

1820
01:28:52,270 --> 01:28:54,431
even when she seems a bit cold.

1821
01:28:55,776 --> 01:28:59,040
(Jin Woo deliberating in his room for a
long time before sending the Love QR)

1822
01:29:00,166 --> 01:29:01,464
("You must be tired. Sleep tight.")

1823
01:29:01,465 --> 01:29:04,052
(He opened the door of his room
and took a picture.)

1824
01:29:04,876 --> 01:29:08,043
I sent the QR to Ji Hye.

1825
01:29:08,422 --> 01:29:09,411
Because...

1826
01:29:09,950 --> 01:29:14,233
She is the closest to my ideal type,
looks-wise.

1827
01:29:14,460 --> 01:29:17,564
So I want to spend more time...

1828
01:29:19,306 --> 01:29:21,025
with Ji Hye.

1829
01:29:22,205 --> 01:29:23,633
Isn't Jin Woo funny?

1830
01:29:23,898 --> 01:29:26,728
He picked Yu Jin for his first impression,
went Talk Room with Ju Hee,

1831
01:29:26,752 --> 01:29:28,976
and then said Ji Hye is his ideal type.

1832
01:29:29,251 --> 01:29:30,874
Gosh, he's so cute.

1833
01:29:30,875 --> 01:29:32,366
(So cute!)

1834
01:29:32,585 --> 01:29:35,245
From now on, I want Jin Woo
to keep his thoughts to himself.

1835
01:29:35,816 --> 01:29:36,592
He's so cute.

1836
01:29:36,617 --> 01:29:38,905
In case a new person might come.

1837
01:29:40,721 --> 01:29:44,700
(The 7th guest in the QR Room is
Ji Seung.)

1838
01:29:46,805 --> 01:29:47,905
(Looking around)

1839
01:29:48,194 --> 01:29:49,401
(Looking around)

1840
01:29:52,299 --> 01:29:53,526
(Anticipation)

1841
01:29:58,842 --> 01:30:00,083
How do I do this?

1842
01:30:01,252 --> 01:30:03,010
I think these two sent it to each other.

1843
01:30:03,035 --> 01:30:06,146
There is no way they haven't.
It's certain.

1844
01:30:07,447 --> 01:30:08,902
(Ji Seung received
the photo of a wine bottle.)

1845
01:30:08,903 --> 01:30:11,527
It was a photo of wine.

1846
01:30:12,251 --> 01:30:15,489
I think that might be Si Won.

1847
01:30:16,132 --> 01:30:20,961
We briefly talked about wine in passing.

1848
01:30:22,615 --> 01:30:25,670
(Who is the younger man who sent
the Love QR to Ji Seung?)

1849
01:30:26,851 --> 01:30:29,870
Since we talked about our taste of wine
at the gathering...

1850
01:30:30,471 --> 01:30:33,540
I thought she might know it's me
if I send a photo of wine.

1851
01:30:35,452 --> 01:30:37,811
They've talked about the wine.

1852
01:30:42,014 --> 01:30:46,580
("Thank you for making me feel
at ease at the start.")

1853
01:30:47,888 --> 01:30:50,920
(A vague message,
hard to tell who sent it)

1854
01:30:52,752 --> 01:30:55,952
I haven't particularly tried
to ease anyone's nerves.

1855
01:30:58,297 --> 01:31:02,135
Still, I hope it's from Ji Seung today.

1856
01:31:04,438 --> 01:31:08,342
(The person who sent the QR
to Si Won was Ji Seung)

1857
01:31:09,041 --> 01:31:10,977
- Shall I help with something here, too?
- It's okay.

1858
01:31:11,891 --> 01:31:14,581
He was the first one
to strike up a conversation.

1859
01:31:15,551 --> 01:31:19,953
He seemed to pay attention
to even the smallest things.

1860
01:31:19,985 --> 01:31:23,768
Because of that, my nerves settled down
quite a bit.

1861
01:31:24,041 --> 01:31:25,753
I wish tomorrow would come already...

1862
01:31:25,777 --> 01:31:29,096
so that I can go on a new date.

1863
01:31:29,121 --> 01:31:30,063
They look good together.

1864
01:31:30,530 --> 01:31:34,685
(Constantly changing minds,
an unpredictable first night)

1865
01:31:38,251 --> 01:31:39,912
(Next to the lounge,
the deepest part of Yeon House)

1866
01:31:39,937 --> 01:31:41,183
(There's the Secret Room.)

1867
01:31:41,208 --> 01:31:42,560
There must be a hint.

1868
01:31:42,585 --> 01:31:43,710
To guess.

1869
01:31:44,288 --> 01:31:47,030
Oh, they can find out information
from there?

1870
01:31:47,055 --> 01:31:48,448
I think there will be some hints.

1871
01:31:48,449 --> 01:31:50,924
(A place that opens only
for the person with the most Love QRs)

1872
01:31:52,285 --> 01:31:54,512
(Open the drawer and guess the age
of the person you are curious about.)

1873
01:31:54,513 --> 01:31:55,829
(What you find out should
remain a secret.)

1874
01:31:56,256 --> 01:32:00,689
(The Secret Room has opened.)

1875
01:32:03,463 --> 01:32:10,219
(Who will be the first person
to open the drawer?)

1876
01:32:14,794 --> 01:32:17,417
(The one who enters the Secret Room is...)

1877
01:32:17,417 --> 01:32:17,967
(Ji Hye.)

1878
01:32:17,967 --> 01:32:18,770
Ji Hye.

1879
01:32:21,760 --> 01:32:25,569
(Ji Hye, who received 2 Love QRs
from Jun Han and Jin Woo)

1880
01:32:26,531 --> 01:32:30,330
(Which of the younger man Ji Hye wants
to know about?)

1881
01:32:30,355 --> 01:32:31,391
Who could it be?

1882
01:32:32,782 --> 01:32:37,659
(What will Ji Hye's choice be?)

1883
01:32:37,964 --> 01:32:40,460
(The second day morning,
the younger men's Choice Date)

1884
01:32:41,203 --> 01:32:43,053
(Today's date is first-come, first-served)

1885
01:32:43,078 --> 01:32:44,765
- First-come, first-served?
- First-come, first-served. I'm going.

1886
01:32:44,790 --> 01:32:45,872
I'm going too.

1887
01:32:46,073 --> 01:32:48,683
(The younger men leaving
without hesitation)

1888
01:32:49,145 --> 01:32:52,345
I left right away
because I wanted to secure my date.

1889
01:32:52,376 --> 01:32:53,298
(Knock, knock)

1890
01:32:53,424 --> 01:32:55,348
Would you like to go on a date
with me today?

1891
01:32:55,811 --> 01:32:57,035
Let's go on a date.

1892
01:32:58,598 --> 01:33:00,687
(Rekindling the excitement
they had forgotten)

1893
01:33:01,418 --> 01:33:04,658
(Building the first memory
between the two of them)

1894
01:33:05,485 --> 01:33:06,827
Your smile is really pretty.

1895
01:33:07,592 --> 01:33:08,730
(Their feelings are growing.)

1896
01:33:08,731 --> 01:33:09,796
We had a lot in common.

1897
01:33:10,465 --> 01:33:11,998
Have you dated a younger guy before?

1898
01:33:12,404 --> 01:33:13,500
Why do you ask?

1899
01:33:13,944 --> 01:33:15,135
Do you want to be the one?

1900
01:33:16,338 --> 01:33:17,838
It's so pretty here.

1901
01:33:18,371 --> 01:33:19,739
But you are prettier.

1902
01:33:20,810 --> 01:33:22,929
(Bold flirting
that only a younger man could pull off)

1903
01:33:23,844 --> 01:33:27,016
(Meanwhile,
a sports car is cutting through the road.)

1904
01:33:29,345 --> 01:33:31,445
I plan to go straight for it
without playing any games.

1905
01:33:32,726 --> 01:33:35,862
(The appearance of a new older woman
who will shake up Yeon House)

1906
01:33:37,311 --> 01:33:39,859
Everyone, sorry for the intrusion.

1907
01:33:39,860 --> 01:33:40,860
Dramaday.me

